    {\cf8\b print}({\cf2 '}{\cf10\b \\n}{\cf2 The date is: \{\}}{\cf2 '}{\cf4 .}format(date{\cf4 .}strftime({\cf2 '}{\cf2 %}{\cf2 B }{\cf9\b %d}{\cf2 , }{\cf2 %}{\cf2 Y}{\cf2 '})))\par
